1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 27=

3
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:16,160
Xiangshan.

4
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:17,559
You're back.

5
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:25,359
Everything we need is ready.

6
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:28,440
Are we leaving tonight,

7
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:29,359
or at dawn?

8
00:00:30,679 --> 00:00:31,559
You go on ahead.

9
00:00:32,119 --> 00:00:32,719
Father...

10
00:00:36,799 --> 00:00:37,679
Go on.

11
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:39,240
I'll catch up with you later.

12
00:00:39,719 --> 00:00:41,799
This time, our family

13
00:00:42,119 --> 00:00:43,200
must stay together.

14
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:44,920
We'll wait for you.

15
00:00:45,719 --> 00:00:46,320
Alright then.

16
00:00:50,039 --> 00:00:53,240
An investigation into Mao Buyu,
Deputy of the Arrest Corps.

17
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:56,079
For openly defying a superior
and using disrespectful language,

18
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,439
he deserves punishment.

19
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:59,580
But considering his record
of solving cases

20
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:00,920
and capturing thieves,

21
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,520
his merits offset his faults.

22
00:01:02,759 --> 00:01:05,280
(Deduction of three months' salary)
By the grace of Vice Minister Zhou

23
00:01:05,300 --> 00:01:07,680
and Commissioner Luo,
Mao Buyu is fined three months' salary

24
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,239
as a warning to others.

25
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,359
Thank goodness it's over.

26
00:01:12,799 --> 00:01:13,480
That was close.

27
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:13,920
It was.

28
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:16,640
We owe thanks to the Commissioner
and the Vice Minister.

29
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:17,990
Alright, that's enough.

30
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:20,760
Just do your job from now on.

31
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:23,120
Remember this lesson.

32
00:01:24,159 --> 00:01:25,719
- Come on, eat up.
- Let's eat.

33
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:26,280
Good.

34
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:27,959
Hold this for me.

35
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,319
Normally,

36
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,760
any slip-up would get us crushed.

37
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,120
But look at Mao Buyu.

38
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,280
He only lost three months' salary.

39
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:39,879
Does the Gate Bureau
even have rules anymore?

40
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:40,719
Exactly.

41
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:41,799
Who needs rules?

42
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,040
He's the one Ms. Luo has her eye on.

43
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,480
Once she becomes

44
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:48,480
the Gate Bureau's
first female Commissioner,

45
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,920
he'll be the Commissioner's husband.

46
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,280
How can we compete with that?

47
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,840
- Too true.
- You're right!

48
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,120
Dong!

49
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:56,990
What did you just say?

50
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,120
Well, if it isn't our happy groom!

51
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:04,560
Allow me to pay my respects.

52
00:02:05,159 --> 00:02:06,120
Looking for a fight?

53
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,040
Not at all.

54
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,719
I wouldn't dream

55
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:11,599
of picking a fight
with our future Commissioner's husband.

56
00:02:13,462 --> 00:02:14,182
Am I right?

57
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:15,680
- Right.
- Of course.

58
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,719
Is there anything you wouldn't do,
Constable Dong?

59
00:02:18,090 --> 00:02:19,560
- Good day, Deputy Luo.
- Deputy Luo.

60
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:23,800
All you ever do is gather around

61
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:26,479
to gossip and talk behind people's backs.

62
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,599
Don't you have work to do?

63
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,159
Are all your cases solved?

64
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:33,360
Get out!

65
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,280
Move, move!

66
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,120
If I hear another word of this,

67
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:38,840
you'll regret it.

68
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,159
Yu...

69
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:54,319
Yu...

70
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,719
They were making baseless claims.

71
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,240
Don't let it get to you.

72
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,520
But everything they said is true.

73
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,919
How am I supposed to ignore that?

74
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:09,240
I know you're still bitter.

75
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:12,879
But think about it, Buyu.

76
00:03:13,010 --> 00:03:14,687
The Mao family is
a lineage of constables

77
00:03:14,687 --> 00:03:16,630
that has served
the Gate Bureau for generations.

78
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,199
Your reputation has been spotless.

79
00:03:19,437 --> 00:03:20,639
Surely you wouldn't want

80
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:22,719
to be the one who destroys the legacy

81
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,719
your ancestors built.

82
00:03:29,919 --> 00:03:30,560
Buyu.

83
00:03:33,090 --> 00:03:35,039
You're at a crossroads
in your life right now.

84
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:36,790
You can't afford
to take a single wrong step.

85
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:39,590
As much as you love Chu Yunchang,
she's still a thief.

86
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:40,879
And you're a constable.

87
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:42,879
The two of you will
never be happy together.

88
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:47,000
The only one who can give you a future,
bring you success,

89
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,120
and restore the Mao family's honor

90
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,159
is me.

91
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:26,600
Yunchang.

92
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,920
I told you not to follow me!

93
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:33,240
Father, I want to go with you.

94
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,399
You might need backup.

95
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:35,720
Go back now.

96
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,600
Help your aunt pack for the trip.

97
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,240
I'm going with you!

98
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:40,839
You...

99
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,199
And me too! I'm coming!

100
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,879
You'll only get in my way!

101
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,839
I've caused so much trouble,

102
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,319
yet she wasn't even mad at me.

103
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,639
So from this day on,

104
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:57,000
wherever she goes, I go.

105
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,120
I'm never leaving her side.

106
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,000
The Gate Bureau is a den of lions.

107
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,160
If something goes wrong,

108
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:03,839
we can be each other's backup.

109
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:04,399
Are you...

110
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:10,879
Fine.

111
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,399
But you must do exactly what I say.

112
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:21,240
The two of you wait for me here.

113
00:05:22,279 --> 00:05:23,399
Zhizhi, stay back for backup.

114
00:05:23,879 --> 00:05:24,879
I'll go with you, Father.

115
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:25,839
Chang.

116
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:28,199
I'm not heading into a battle.

117
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,290
Going alone draws less attention.

118
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:32,637
Just wait for me here.

119
00:05:51,912 --> 00:05:54,912
(Review Bureau)

120
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:56,040
Shun.

121
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:59,360
Any progress on the investigation
I gave you the other day?

122
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:01,612
There are many case files to go through.

123
00:06:01,612 --> 00:06:02,773
I haven't found a lead yet.

124
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,399
What's wrong?

125
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,399
I think I ate something bad.

126
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:10,120
Go take care of it.

127
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,480
But aren't we on night patrol?

128
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:15,000
I can handle it myself.

129
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:16,600
That doesn't seem right.

130
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:18,560
I'll stay with Master.

131
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,319
You go ahead.

132
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:21,079
Thanks, Wuxia.

133
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:21,920
I'll get going.

134
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,680
No problem.

135
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,399
Master.

136
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,100
Let me carry that for you.

137
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:29,600
Let's go.

138
00:07:16,650 --> 00:07:18,162
(Token)

139
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:26,162
(Token)

140
00:07:33,337 --> 00:07:34,087
(Token)

141
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,720
What's taking him so long?

142
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,879
He only just went in.

143
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:04,879
Is that so?

144
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:10,000
Think about it.

145
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,639
This place is massive.

146
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:14,399
With so many rooms,
he has to search them one by one.

147
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:18,000
He even has to check
the Commissioner's room.

148
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:20,279
It will take a while.

149
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:23,160
I've got a bad feeling about this.

150
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,759
I have to check on him.

151
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,199
Be honest with me.

152
00:08:27,519 --> 00:08:29,240
Are you actually worried,

153
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:32,720
or are you just missing someone inside?

154
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,320
You've moved on from a heartbreak,

155
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,519
so you're rubbing it in?

156
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:37,960
I wouldn't dare.

157
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:39,879
Wait here.

158
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,000
I'll go to my father.

159
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:41,960
But...

160
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,840
Just do as I say.

161
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,600
That's an order.

162
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,480
Is what you told me

163
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,360
the truth?

164
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:58,720
I'd hate to see them get in any deeper.

165
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:01,679
They are your family.

166
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,210
Why are you helping Yunchang?

167
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,120
Personally,

168
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,159
I have feelings for Ms. Yunchang.

169
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:11,360
But professionally,
I'm just doing what's right.

170
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,639
What's right?

171
00:09:14,825 --> 00:09:15,785
You've really grown up.

172
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,159
Master.

173
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,399
Tell me the truth.

174
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,600
Do you have
another identity and mission?

175
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:25,399
Nonsense.

176
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,240
Fine, keep your secrets.

177
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,279
But please,

178
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,720
show some mercy
to my grandfather and Wushuang

179
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:36,639
when the time comes.

180
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:43,360
Who's there?

181
00:09:43,475 --> 00:09:44,519
(Upright and Honest)

182
00:09:44,519 --> 00:09:45,080
Master!

183
00:09:58,919 --> 00:09:59,559
Chang.

184
00:10:11,159 --> 00:10:12,279
How bold of you to come here.

185
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,159
We just came back
to look into a few things.

186
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,480
"We"?

187
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:17,960
Who else is with you?

188
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:20,519
My father and I.

189
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,320
We're here to confirm something.

190
00:10:23,519 --> 00:10:25,720
Your disregard
for the law is unbelievable.

191
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,799
Have me arrested, then.

192
00:10:33,770 --> 00:10:35,440
You know perfectly well
I'd never do that.

193
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:41,840
I didn't come here to start any trouble.

194
00:10:42,519 --> 00:10:44,120
I just want to help my father get away.

195
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:49,519
After tonight,
you won't ever have to see me again.

196
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,559
Are you leaving with your father?

197
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:55,679
What choice do I have?

198
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:57,879
Stay here and wait to be arrested?

199
00:11:00,519 --> 00:11:01,200
So...

200
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,080
So tonight is...

201
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,159
This is farewell.

202
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,360
Can I ask you one last question?

203
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,559
If you still trust me,
just give me a little more time.

204
00:11:32,050 --> 00:11:33,039
What are you going to do?

205
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:34,080
Find the truth.

206
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,639
I'm out of time.

207
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,350
I must get my father out of the Capital.

208
00:11:40,487 --> 00:11:44,537
♪Donning a mask to hide my heart♪

209
00:11:44,575 --> 00:11:47,537
♪Playing a part with a hollow smile♪

210
00:11:48,537 --> 00:11:51,900
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

211
00:11:52,575 --> 00:11:56,475
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

212
00:11:56,550 --> 00:12:00,387
♪A love so deep,
yet destiny so fleeting♪

213
00:12:00,612 --> 00:12:03,387
♪This fervor is buried deep within♪

214
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:05,559
I'm running out of time.

215
00:12:06,039 --> 00:12:07,279
I must leave with my father.

216
00:12:07,279 --> 00:12:08,200
I'll come along.

217
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,399
That can't be wise.

218
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:11,639
I know very well

219
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:12,639
what to do

220
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,559
and when to do it.

221
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,519
Let me be reckless one last time.

222
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:21,960
Chang.

223
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,559
Take your father and get out of here.

224
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:24,720
I'll keep watch at the door.

225
00:12:24,775 --> 00:12:27,813
♪I end up creating another knot instead♪

226
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:43,840
Father...

227
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:46,200
Father?

228
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:48,679
Father?

229
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:50,919
Father!

230
00:12:52,879 --> 00:12:54,519
Father!

231
00:12:57,679 --> 00:13:00,360
Father! Open your eyes!

232
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:03,799
Father!

233
00:13:05,279 --> 00:13:07,679
Wake up!

234
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,080
Father!

235
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,399
Father!

236
00:13:16,639 --> 00:13:18,919
I'm here for you, Father.

237
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:22,559
Father...

238
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:27,960
Father?

239
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:33,879
Father...

240
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:34,360
Father?

241
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,039
Father...

242
00:13:36,039 --> 00:13:36,919
What happened?

243
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,039
Father, wake up! Please!

244
00:13:40,559 --> 00:13:41,200
Father!

245
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:42,960
Father!

246
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:44,639
Father!

247
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,159
Father!

248
00:13:49,759 --> 00:13:51,600
I'll save you, Father!

249
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:53,639
Father!

250
00:13:56,679 --> 00:13:57,639
Father!

251
00:13:58,799 --> 00:13:59,720
Father!

252
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:02,240
How did this happen?

253
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,440
Please wake up!

254
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:05,679
Wake up, Father!

255
00:14:05,919 --> 00:14:06,480
Father!

256
00:14:07,679 --> 00:14:08,360
Father!

257
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:13,712
(Noble Character)

258
00:14:13,762 --> 00:14:18,337
(Inspiring Integrity)

259
00:14:18,375 --> 00:14:20,812
(Noble Character)

260
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:24,437
(Noble Character)

261
00:14:30,087 --> 00:14:31,675
(Inspiring Integrity)

262
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:33,639
Wushuang!

263
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,960
What's going on?

264
00:14:35,399 --> 00:14:36,559
Why are there so many people?

265
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,960
(Inspiring Integrity)
Has a thief broken into the Gate Bureau?

266
00:14:44,679 --> 00:14:46,120
Chu Yunchang, you're not going...

267
00:14:50,159 --> 00:14:50,879
Wake up!

268
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:52,679
Father!

269
00:14:57,759 --> 00:14:58,440
Father...

270
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,480
Uncle Mao!

271
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:06,960
Chu Yunchang!

272
00:15:07,679 --> 00:15:09,200
I received a tip to arrest you.

273
00:15:09,512 --> 00:15:10,392
But you...

274
00:15:11,759 --> 00:15:13,600
You and your family
have killed Uncle Mao!

275
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,200
Please, look at me...

276
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:17,759
Yu.

277
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,919
You must avenge Uncle Mao!

278
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,759
How can this be happening?

279
00:15:30,279 --> 00:15:30,879
Father!

280
00:15:31,159 --> 00:15:31,759
Yu!

281
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:32,919
Father!

282
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,820
Are you going
to ignore Uncle Mao's death

283
00:15:35,519 --> 00:15:37,240
just because of this woman?

284
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:41,500
Take this.

285
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:58,025
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

286
00:15:58,063 --> 00:16:00,938
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

287
00:16:01,438 --> 00:16:07,156
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

288
00:16:08,338 --> 00:16:11,658
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

289
00:16:11,788 --> 00:16:14,708
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

290
00:16:15,876 --> 00:16:21,116
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

291
00:16:22,338 --> 00:16:24,731
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

292
00:16:24,731 --> 00:16:28,381
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

293
00:16:28,450 --> 00:16:31,940
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

294
00:16:32,038 --> 00:16:35,013
♪To the ends of time♪

295
00:16:35,013 --> 00:16:38,388
♪The moon traces your face♪

296
00:16:38,575 --> 00:16:42,163
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

297
00:16:42,163 --> 00:16:48,403
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

298
00:16:48,738 --> 00:16:51,953
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

299
00:16:52,238 --> 00:16:55,776
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

300
00:16:56,063 --> 00:16:59,088
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

301
00:16:59,088 --> 00:17:02,188
♪On our way to forever♪

302
00:17:02,188 --> 00:17:06,038
♪The moon traces your face♪

303
00:17:06,038 --> 00:17:09,398
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

304
00:17:09,588 --> 00:17:15,548
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

305
00:17:16,625 --> 00:17:26,265
♪Just to be with you♪
